Package: SIRSsim
Title: SIRS Model Simulator
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Austin", "Melendez", , "austinmelendez@csus.edu", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Author: Austin Melendez [aut, cre]
Maintainer: Austin Melendez <austinmelendez@csus.edu>
Description: Allows simulation runs of disease spread with SIR, SIS, and SIRS model options. Optionally enable death, immunity to disease after infection, and customize probabilities for each parameter.
